 />\n連登之所以出現<br />\n係因為林早泄太廢<br />\n<br />\n話熱狗霸左高登都痴線<br />\n高登連登一向多打手<br />\n熱狗只係打手中一少堆人<br />\n熱狗何德何能趕走到人另起爐灶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇熱普城各人嘅下場<br />\n都幾肯定係內鬼<br />\n專分化反對派嘅人同𠝹票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算撐唔撐本土<br />\n我都唔會撐熱狗<br />\n亦一定唔會撐垃圾林早泄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算連登日後摺左<br />\n我都唔會撐林早泄搞嘅任何野<br />\n佢覺悟得太遲<br />\n之前賺咁多廣告費都唔搞好高登<br />\n仲要依家成日搵D打手開新post黎惡意唱衰連登<br />\n呢D屎橋稍為上網耐D都睇得穿<br />\n<br />\n我覺得連登好用<br />\n理撚得佢連尼住政治立場係乜呀<br />\n佢同佢partner確實係搞個網站同app好<br />\n<br />\n正如阿信屋同九方我都覺得好就照幫襯<br />\n唔會理佢老細係咪親共<br />\n上個網站用個app都要睇個老細係乜政治立場<br />\n你會唔會想多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你自己咁劃地自限<br />\n就玩高登玩到過世<br />\n千萬唔好再玩連登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好左右其他連登仔<br />\n上乜網站同用乜app完全係個人自由黎"},{"pid":"1d85eab510c2e8f4735eaf9f9176d324f79e8257","tid":350694,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T13:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢樣真<br />\n<br />\n你睇下熱狗係連登個待遇慘過高登幾多就知<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢哋幾個大將軍唔識過河<img src