br />\n你同D大陸人係外國住<br />\n但話外國有幾差過中國有乜分別<br />\n口裡說不<br />\n但身體卻很誠實</blockquote><br />\n我點解無啦啦要番高登?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125e7466fc644ae65edd0e2521c01f0406818595","tid":350694,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T13:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/212721_5590ea50c574bf4f9f22a539f681c7af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F212721_5590ea50c574bf4f9f22a539f681c7af.jpg&h=8b7ca3a9&s={SIZE}\" />恭喜你個pist成功上左熱門，我地睇下會唔會俾人攞返落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一晌熱門度跌番出嚟, 就可以大條道理話連尼住滅聲了, yeah! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750ebbfae9142a293774efa4f1b0195cd827cea8","tid":350694,"uid":7371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T13:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/212721_5590ea50c574bf4f9f22a539f681c7af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F212721_5590ea50c574bf4f9f22a539f681c7af.jpg&h=8b7ca3a9&s={SIZE}\" />恭喜你個pist成功上左熱門，我地睇下會唔會俾人攞返落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為呢個係新acc黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你覺得連登唔係樂土<br />\n<br />\n就唔好再係連登開新acc"},{"pid":"59fc1aa75ed2dffe888581e51f51ff1c0b99bc98","tid":350694,"uid":124338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T13:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/212721_5590ea50c574bf4f9f22a539f681c7af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F212721_5590ea50c574bf4f9f22a539f681c7af.jpg&h=8b7ca3a9&s={SIZE}\" />恭喜你個pist成功上左熱門，我地睇下會唔會俾人攞返落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一晌熱門度跌番出嚟, 就可以大條道理話連尼住滅聲了, yeah! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前個acc專登刷負評要刷到600先有粒閃電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3fd564db57884a7ea089b7603d3ea6bd37474f","tid":350694,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T13:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主<br />\n<br />\n你要証明你講嘅野係對<br />\n你就一定要堅定地剩玩高登<br />\n唔好再上連登<br />\n唔好再係連登留言同出post<br />\n<br />\n如果自己都做唔到<br />\n就唔好學人叫人做D乜<br />\n<br />\n你同D大陸人係外國住<br />\n但話外國有幾差過中國有乜分別<br />\n口裡說不<br />\n但身體卻很誠實</blockquote><br />\n我點解無啦啦要番高登?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你已經做左選擇<br />\n事後就話連登唔係樂土<br />\n你真係慳D啦"},{"pid":"5ea15f1a6453decf3177d3242ff2bdfcb776d42a","tid":350694,"uid":59609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T13:31:36.000Z","msg":"樓主，你知道得太多了。"},{"pid":"1cfe9367cd86a15f2d6ae48d8c6d9762d5d77924","tid":350694,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T13:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登之所以出現，其實係因為青政俾熱狗係高登打到完全冇哂地盤<br />\n連登close beta最先流傳既地方就係各個青政/本土(親青政)地區組織既telegram group<br />\n<br />\n連尼住一開始係想將自己推到做KOL，即係好似容癌之列，可惜個人魅力唔夠俾人打左落台就專心做番it9<br />\n<br />\n另外講開又講，連尼住同容癌關係有幾密切，你留意下容癌同佢一眾手下facebook就會發現<br />\n<br />\n連登目的真係唔係為左賺錢，而係在於可以控制邊個有權講野</blockquote><br />\n求其鳩up幾隻字就當係真&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n最少都cap幾張&quot;最先流傳既地方就係各個青政/本土(親青政)地區組織既telegram group&quot;嘅圖嚟睇下先啦.</blockquote><br />\n驚樓主睇唔到, reply多次先~"},{"pid":"ca6226b2560966ce516a69cdf244bb2b82ee4270","tid":350694,"uid":21249,"li